Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.98,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.74,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,You made all these? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:15.99,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,It's really not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.54,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. You're amazing, Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.59,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:33.86,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all the magic I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.34,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing, Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:44.98,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.64,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:49.90,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.90,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.34,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.66,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,If you wouldn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.80,flashbacktop,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,May I come over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.80,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:11.80,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:18.01,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,There we go. All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.84,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take over for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:31.57,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,And to finish it off... a pinch\N of moguro leaf powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:39.73,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Slower, gentler... Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:41.71,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.21,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.56,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Now they won't get chapped so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.00,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:52.96,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:54.81,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.28,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.08,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.10,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.88,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,They did this. They asked \Nto see my catalyst magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.99,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,They only wanted to see me fail and laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:22.44,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,He almost looked worried \Nand asked, "Are you okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.82,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,But I know he was laughing on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:28.25,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,They're all like that. They're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.62,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.75,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,And so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.21,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.47,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it. It'll get better soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.25,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.22,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.03,flashback,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:48.83,flashback,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:55.40,italics,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.64,italics,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.56,italics,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,I lived in a world where the sun didn't shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:09.11,italics,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,We were weak and fleeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.16,italics,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,But we definitely existed.
